{"tid":1736340,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術分享] 美國文獻證明警察智力唔可以太高！","createTime":"2019-11-18T17:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T09:36:43.000Z","uid":304921,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2682395475284f912af47ed0027aec16300b08","tid":1736340,"uid":304921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"深夜訓唔著<br />\n睇住班警察做埋啲低能野好難唔相信佢地弱智<br />\n腦入面忽然諗<br />\n究竟有無人真係研究過popo的IQ有幾多呢？<br />\n<br />\n結果上網一查，原來美國有人研究過警察平均智力只有104。更驚訝的係，原來<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>IQ test係用黎篩選警察<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>-[red]IQ太高，係唔可以做警察！［/red]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以美國Connecticut為例<br />\n投考警察等人 IQ Test 要21-27分的範圍人先可以進入下一輪面試 (21分等如IQ104）<br />\n<br />\n2000年的時候，有一位49歲去面試警察的男人得到33分（即係IQ125)的成績，點知連下一輪面試都無，結果入稟法院&mdash;「點解IQ Test幾好都無得落下一輪面試？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，警方公佈只有分數位於21-27分的應徵者先會有面試。21-22分等如IQ104，太高分係唔會請你。<br />\n<br />\n最好笑的係法院判美國警方勝訴，原因係IQ比較低的警察，無咁易轉工(lower turnover rate)咁話；而IQ高的應徵者，好快會因為沈悶的工作內容離職。咁又係嘅，淨係接上頭的Order，唔洗用腦諗野思考，依類工真係智力要夠低先會想做。<br />\n<br />\n結論係：<span style=\"color: orange;\">警察IQ唔會高，研究都支持！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文如下：<a href=\"https://www.globalresearch.ca/us-court-ruled-you-can-be-too-smart-to-be-a-cop/5420630/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalresearch.ca%2Fus-court-ruled-you-can-be-too-smart-to-be-a-cop%2F5420630%2Famp&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZVzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=c417a809\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.globalresearch.ca/us-court-ruled-you-can-be-too-smart-to-be-a-cop/5420630/amp</a><br />\n<br />\nCan a person actually be &ldquo;too smart&rdquo; to be a cop in America?<br />\n<br />\nA federal court&rsquo;s decision back in 2000 suggests that, yes, you actually can be.<br />\n<br />\nRobert Jordan, a 49-year-old college graduate, scored a 33 on an intelligence test he took as part of the application process to become a police officer in the town of New London, Connecticut. The score meant Jordan had an IQ of 125.<br />\n<br />\nThe average score for police officers was a 21-22, or an IQ of 104. New London would only interview candidates who scored between 20 and 27.<br />\n<br />\nJordan sued the city alleging discrimination, but the 2nd U.S. Circuit Court of Appeals in New York upheld that it wasn&rsquo;t discrimination. &ldquo;Why?&rdquo; you might ask. Because New London Police Department applied the same standard to everyone who applied to be a cop there.<br />\n<br />\nAnd the theory behind it?<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Those who scored too high could get bored with police work and leave soon after undergoing costly training,&rdquo; ABC News reported back then. While at least acknowledging the basic fact that such a policy might be &ldquo;unwise,&rdquo; the court deemed it had a &ldquo;rational basis&rdquo; because it was put in place to lower cop turnover.<br />\n<br />\nThe police department went on to continue automatically disqualifying anyone whose IQ was &ldquo;too high.&rdquo; Jordan went on to become a prison guard instead."},{"pid":"371f4f709b6001356547243aa84c403d7243eb75","tid":1736340,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:35:17.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"02247107e53a7f0992d766d2ecd442001514a0bd","tid":1736340,"uid":105678,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"不嬲，香港警察面試有條問題係你點睇班近日示威事件，答得太認真係會畀人foul，求其答下支持警察執法示威者正仆街就會過到面試<br />\n<br />\n擺到明就專收社會冇腦嘅垃圾，因為佢地冇能力in到同薪酬嘅其他工種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e0ace0ddf3747cd117f4b950b476a91e18f4e8","tid":1736340,"uid":129895,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"香港唔同美國, 香港d警犬智商大約80"},{"pid":"9a0cfb0eb100435c1eb7a64fe8a3bf809d88a3e4","tid":1736340,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:03:34.000Z","msg":"說穿了咪姐係弱智都可以管班市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你再聰明都要睇班弱智仔頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果打算因為咁而笑班狗的話我肯定佢地笑得大聲過你"},{"pid":"6f857a28c3c13aca9c17862907a53a021dce3237","tid":1736340,"uid":304921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02247107e53a7f0992d766d2ecd442001514a0bd","tid":1736340,"uid":105678,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"不嬲，香港警察面試有條問題係你點睇班近日示威事件，答得太認真係會畀人foul，求其答下支持警察執法示威者正仆街就會過到面試<br />\n<br />\n擺到明就專收社會冇腦嘅垃圾，因為佢地冇能力in到同薪酬嘅其他工種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:07:58.000Z","msg":"高薪養豬"},{"pid":"81b5e772ef21b05bcccc3d79eadf83ba34176268","tid":1736340,"uid":304921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"77e0ace0ddf3747cd117f4b950b476a91e18f4e8","tid":1736340,"uid":129895,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"香港唔同美國, 香港d警犬智商大約80"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:10:52.000Z","msg":"80都高得濟😂"},{"pid":"379a3b5f6a9accbc5f28a3abaf114ef273ddb4f5","tid":1736340,"uid":304921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9a0cfb0eb100435c1eb7a64fe8a3bf809d88a3e4","tid":1736340,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:03:34.000Z","msg":"說穿了咪姐係弱智都可以管班市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你再聰明都要睇班弱智仔頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果打算因為咁而笑班狗的話我肯定佢地笑得大聲過你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"傻啦 唔洗文獻都笑緊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係想話依d前線執行角色IQ係咁上下 世界大同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國狗 國民都好憎<br />\n但7到香港狗咁 就史無前例喇"},{"pid":"6af64efeec583807146e3e25659902bac6208116","tid":1736340,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"做高官IQ 都唔高得"},{"pid":"a3cbc26caf4fc4a0ab6f53900246938f2d959629","tid":1736340,"uid":79228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0ec3a194ff2398f7b11723dce156b4400faf9e","tid":1736340,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:45:52.000Z","msg":"香港警察的問題唔係iq太高 而係iq太低"},{"pid":"fe6ed55b9e08c64e2983e5951b664ce5c1be38dc","tid":1736340,"uid":247946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:50:54.000Z","msg":"唔准你哋再笑popo弱智仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e948bb6287be6b9554a522c3a68863395ce86eb","tid":1736340,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"難怪入面冇黃警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa95605fc75a281a5f522f7c978368c3e5267165","tid":1736340,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"依個網好似鳩up o架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46f8362114d214e70a0e1828463588b56d2d2ca","tid":1736340,"uid":60748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"垃圾智障毅進狗智商低都正常"},{"pid":"ee22a6bd8b1b8abd2f9c2f063cf501896c4efa0b","tid":1736340,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"正確<br />\n正如小學學歷才可做國家主席"},{"pid":"d8d6adbf7a4f1b723e27c18b2988840b5c2a3322","tid":1736340,"uid":304921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa95605fc75a281a5f522f7c978368c3e5267165","tid":1736340,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:24:24.000Z","msg":"依個網好似鳩up o架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"多謝告知<br />\n我fact check左一下，個court case 同都係真的，原文係度：<a href=\"http://www.aele.org/apa/jordan-newlondon.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aele.org%2Fapa%2Fjordan-newlondon.html&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZVzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=fb0b0170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aele.org/apa/jordan-newlondon.html</a> (Source: AELE)"}]}